title: #509 - Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt
description:
Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio talking about Joey's appearance on the 1,000th "Joe Rogan Experience" podcast, getting and keeping a job in prison, and what it's like to do LSD in prison.
